│   └── images/         # All images
└── _next/static/
    └── css/            # Compiled CSS
```

## Required Elements on All Pages

1. **Google Tag Manager** - in `<head>` and after `<body>`
2. **RB2B Script** - in `<head>`
3. **Signup Attribution Tracking** - before `</body>`
4. **Footer with policy links** - Terms, Privacy, Cookies
5. **Consistent navigation** - Logo, section links, CTAs

## Testing Checklist

Before committing changes:
- [ ] Check mobile responsiveness (especially nav at 880px breakpoint)
- [ ] Verify all links work (especially signup URLs with UTM params)
- [ ] Test Calendly popup functionality
- [ ] Verify FAQ accordions expand/collapse
- [ ] Check color contrast for accessibility
- [ ] Validate HTML (no unclosed tags)
- [ ] Test in multiple browsers

## Performance

- Preload critical images (logo)
- Use lazy loading for below-fold images
- Keep inline JavaScript minimal
- Avoid blocking resources in `<head>`

## Do Not

- Do NOT modify files in `_next/static/chunks/` (legacy Next.js build artifacts)
- Do NOT add React/Next.js hydration - this is a static site
- Do NOT commit .DS_Store files
- Do NOT use external dependencies (CDNs) without approval
- Do NOT remove tracking scripts without discussion
- Do NOT change the CNAME file
